e alsoedit novartis medicines and healthcare products regulatory agency british medical association food and drug administration referencesedit  gsk pharma completes acquisition of novartis healthcares vaccines business pharmaceutical technology retrieved    a b c d e f g lawrence m fisher october   biotechnology spotlight now shines on chiron the new york times   a b chironcetus management the new york times november     chiron to get  million the new york times november     loss at chiron is attributed to ciba alliance the new york times may     a b lawrence m fisher april   a new model for biotechnology the new york times   chiron research unit the new york times october     lawrence m fisher march   specialist in diagnostics now president of chiron the new york times   chironortho pact for du pont unit the new york times january     chiron acquisition the new york times april     andrew pollack july    biotech pioneers to merge the new york times   lawrence m fisher april   price of failure in biotechnology the new york times   chirons president quits the new york times december     chief executive named at chiron the new york times march     chiron hires glaxosmithkline executive as chief the new york times march     john tagliabue september   bayer buying chiron unit and stake in seed venture agfa offering set the new york times   lawrence m fisher december   fda panel recommends approval of a chiron drug the new york times   milt freudenheim july   fda approves a multiple sclerosis drug the new york times   a b chiron company profile the new york times august     fda clears regranex – becaplermin – gel  for diabetic foot ulcers chiron to supply active ingredient to orthomcneil december     a b andrew pollack august   chiron to acquire pathogenesis for  million the new york times   fda approves inhaled antibiotic for management of cystic fibrosis patients fda december     chiron corporation – history   chiron corporation  powderject pharmaceuticals plc uk offi